        <ul>
            <li><strong>Flavour:</strong> None—pure nicotine, mild saline taste from calcium matrix</li>
            <li><strong>Onset:</strong> Unmasked nicotine sensation; rapid and unambiguous</li>
            <li><strong>Duration:</strong> No flavour dissipation; focus is entirely on nicotine delivery</li>
            <li><strong>Best for:</strong> Technical users, minimalists, those seeking "invisible" nicotine, professional settings</li>
