        <p>KLAR Blank offers pure, flavourless nicotine. No sensory theatre, no discretion concerns—just effective delivery. Ideal for office environments where flavoured pouches might be noticed.</p>

        <h3>Users Seeking Lower Total Nicotine</h3>
        <p>Because KLAR's faster onset means equivalent satisfaction at lower doses, you can reduce overall nicotine consumption without sacrificing effectiveness. If reducing nicotine is a goal, KLAR accelerates progress.</p>
