            <li>Shorter effective duration (20–30 min vs. 30–45 min)—you'll use more pouches daily</li>
            <li>Limited flavour range (only Mint + Blank)</li>
            <li>Premium price (higher per-pouch cost than ZYN or Nordic Spirit)</li>
            <li>Newer brand—less market data on long-term user patterns</li>
